<varlistentry id="options.HonorMotifHints">
	<term>HonorMotifHints</term>
	<listitem>
		<para>AfterStep will honor Motif specific hints set on the client's window. This includes any decorations that need to be drawn around it and any functions (minimize/maximize/re-size/move) that it supports. The opposite is NoMotifHints.</para>
		<para>See Also: NoMotifHints.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
